    <title>css学习笔记</title>
    <link href="http://autobyai.com/2019/06/09/css%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <id>http://autobyai.com/2019/06/09/css学习笔记/</id>
    <published>2019-06-09T08:23:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-06-09T10:30:31.388Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="CSS学习笔记"><a href="#CSS学习笔记" class="headerlink" title="CSS学习笔记"></a>CSS学习笔记</h1><h2 id="文本"><a href="#文本" class="headerlink" title="文本"></a>文本</h2><h4 id="文本颜色color"><a href="#文本颜色color" class="headerlink" title="文本颜色color"></a>文本颜色<strong>color</strong></h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">body &#123;color:red;&#125; //颜色名称形式  </span><br><span class="line">h1 &#123;color:#ff0000;&#125; //十六进制颜色值形式  </span><br><span class="line">h2 &#123;color:rgb(255,0,0);&#125; //rgb形式</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="文本对齐text-align"><a href="#文本对齐text-align" class="headerlink" title="文本对齐text-align"></a>文本对齐<strong>text-align</strong></h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">h1 &#123;text-align:center/right/left/justify;&#125; //justify会自动调整左右对齐边框</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="文本修饰text-decoration"><a href="#文本修饰text-decoration" class="headerlink" title="文本修饰text-decoration"></a>文本修饰<strong>text-decoration</strong></h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">h1 &#123;text-decoration:none;&#125; //常用来删除链接的下划线  </span><br><span class="line">h1 &#123;text-decoration:overline/line-through/underline;&#125; //添加文本的上划线、删除线、下划线</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="文本转换text-transform"><a href="#文本转换text-transform" class="headerlink" title="文本转换text-transform"></a>文本转换<strong>text-transform</strong></h4><p>指定特定文本转换为大写、小写或者单词的首字母大写  </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">p.uppercase &#123;text-transform:uppercase;&#125;  //全部转换为大写</span><br><span class="line">p.lowercase &#123;text-transform:lowercase;&#125;  //转换为小写</span><br><span class="line">p.capitalize &#123;text-transform:capitalize;&#125;  //转为为首字母大写</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="文本缩进text-indent"><a href="#文本缩进text-indent" class="headerlink" title="文本缩进text-indent"></a>文本缩进<strong>text-indent</strong></h4><p>文本缩进用来指定文本的第一行的缩进,像素为单位，比如段落的开头  </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">p &#123;text-indent:50px;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="CSS字体"><a href="#CSS字体" class="headerlink" title="CSS字体"></a>CSS字体</h2><p>css字体属性定义字体类型、加粗、大小、文字样式等</p><h4 id="字型font-family"><a href="#字型font-family" class="headerlink" title="字型font-family"></a>字型<strong>font-family</strong></h4><ul><li>通用字体系列–拥有像似外观的字体系统组合（如 “Serif” 、”SansSerif”或 “Monospace”）</li><li>特定子体系列–一个特定的字体系列（如”Times”或”Courier”）<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">p.serif&#123;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Times,serif;&#125; //serif系列，Times New Roman字体</span><br><span class="line">p.sansserif&#123;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&#125; //sans-serif系列，Arial字体，备用Helvetica字体</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h4 id="字体样式font-style"><a href="#字体样式font-style" class="headerlink" title="字体样式font-style"></a>字体样式<strong>font-style</strong></h4><p>主要用于指定斜体文字的字体样式属性  </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">p.normal &#123;font-style:normal;&#125; //正常字体</span><br><span class="line">p.italic &#123;font-style:italic;&#125; //斜体</span><br><span class="line">p.oblique &#123;font-style:oblique;&#125; //倾斜的文字，和斜体类似</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="字体大小font-size"><a href="#字体大小font-size" class="headerlink" title="字体大小font-size"></a>字体大小<strong>font-size</strong></h4><ul><li><p>按照像素定义字体大小</p><blockquote><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;h1 &#123;font-size:40px;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;h2 &#123;font-size:30px;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;p &#123;font-size:14px;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote></li><li><p>按照em来设置字体大小,1em和当前浏览器默认的字体大小相等，一般是16px,但是在IE中可能兼容性不好</p><blockquote><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;h1 &#123;font-size:2.5em;&#125; /* 40px/16=2.5em */</span><br><span class="line">&gt;h2 &#123;font-size:1.875em;&#125; /* 30px/16=1.875em */</span><br><span class="line">&gt;p &#123;font-size:0.875em;&#125; /* 14px/16=0.875em */</span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote></li><li><p>使用百分比和EM组合，可以解决不同浏览器兼容问题，设置 &lt;\body&gt;元素的默认字体大小的是百分比：</p><blockquote><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;body &#123;font-size:100%;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;h1 &#123;font-size:2.5em;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;h2 &#123;font-size:1.875em;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;p &#123;font-size:0.875em;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote></li></ul><h4 id="字体粗细font-weight"><a href="#字体粗细font-weight" class="headerlink" title="字体粗细font-weight"></a>字体粗细<strong>font-weight</strong></h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">p.normal &#123;font-weight:normal;&#125; //正常粗细字体</span><br><span class="line">p.thick &#123;font-weight:bold;&#125; //粗字体</span><br><span class="line">p.thicker &#123;font-weight:900;&#125; //单位900粗细的字体</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="字体转换font-variant"><a href="#字体转换font-variant" class="headerlink" title="字体转换font-variant"></a>字体转换<strong>font-variant</strong></h4><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">p</span><span class="selector-class">.normal</span> &#123;<span class="attribute">font-variant</span>:normal;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">p</span><span class="selector-class">.small</span> &#123;<span class="attribute">font-variant</span>:small-caps;&#125; <span class="comment">/*以小型大写字体或者正常字体显示文本,所有字母大写，首字母大写大字体，其余字母大写小字体*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>显示结果如下：</strong><br>p.normal:<br>My name is Hege Refsnes.<br>p.small:<br>M<sub>Y</sub> N<sub>AME</sub> I<sub>S</sub> H<sub>EGE</sub> R<sub>EFSNES</sub>.</p>]]></content>
    
